name: Dragged by the Dead
description:
Welcome to Serial Dead Body series. 
There was a time, when I am a kid, I can find dead body in place that I used as playground. Sometimes the body wrap in fabric, put in baggage or card-box, sometimes is laying as it is. The smells is awful. Most of the time I curious how the body end up there, how a person can easily killing other person. I also have personal experienced, so I know how killing can destroy the closest one to the victim.

Created by Prasajadi, mint in 2021
